%description
A simple web user interface for the hledger accounting system, providing a more
modern UI than the command-line or terminal interfaces. It can be used as a
local single-user UI, or as a multi-user UI for viewing/adding/editing on the
web.

hledger is a robust, cross-platform set of tools for tracking money, time, or
any other commodity, using double-entry accounting and a simple, editable file
format, with command-line, terminal and web interfaces. It is a Haskell rewrite
of Ledger, and one of the leading implementations of Plain Text Accounting.
Read more at: <https://hledger.org>.


